        "message": "Phase 3: Cinematic immersion + GitHub Pages deployment\n\n- Camera: section-specific lerp speeds, FOV animation, mouse parallax\n- Lighting: hemisphere light, animated directional, rim backlights, procedural caustics\n- Ocean: vertex displacement wave animation\n- LightRays: 12 dynamic rays with sway and opacity pulse\n- Particles: dual-layer floaters + dust\n- Bubbles: 80 bubbles with wobble and size variation\n- Coral: 14 clusters with intact-reactive color fading\n- Seabed: rock formations, 3 debris shapes, pollution colors\n- New: Kelp (swaying seaweed), Fish (instanced schools), Ruins (ancient pillars)\n- World: orchestrates all systems from scene state\n- GitHub Pages workflow with static export",
